" disable backspace, delete, etc
"COMMENTED_BS: disabled backspace on purpose, to get used to C-H
"NOTE: in order to enable BS back, grep for COMMENTED_BS, and you'll get
"other places where you need to uncomment it
":inoremap <BS> <Nop>
":inoremap <Del> <Nop>
":inoremap <PageDown> <Nop>
":inoremap <PageUp> <Nop>
":inoremap <Up> <Nop>
":inoremap <Down> <Nop>
":inoremap <Left> <Nop>
":inoremap <Right> <Nop>
":nnoremap <BS> <Nop>
":nnoremap <Del> <Nop>
":nnoremap <PageDown> <Nop>
":nnoremap <PageUp> <Nop>
":nnoremap <Up> <Nop>
":nnoremap <Down> <Nop>
":nnoremap <Left> <Nop>
":nnoremap <Right> <Nop>

